		{"id":"131fec6abed9e091","x":-185,"y":679,"width":250,"height":801,"type":"text","text":"Overview over:\n- Active leads\n- Vehicles in stock\n- Revenue\n- Customer\n- Revenue trend\n\n---\nSales funnel (Open pipeline) that leads to the Pipeline page.\n\n---\nQuick actions:\n- New leads\n- Add vehicle\n- Purchase order\n\n---\nRecent leads with a view all button that leads to the Pipeline page.\n\n---\nTop selling section with the most top selling motorcycle"},
