		{"id":"9b4886d7892f5844","x":983,"y":700,"width":250,"height":400,"type":"text","text":"The pipeline page has 5 columns with:\n1. New leads\n2. Contacted leads\n3. Test Ride\n4. Negotiating leads\n5. Closed leads\n\n---\nEach customer card leads to a Create Purchase Agreement page (/sales/leads/1/agreement)"},
